 Digital Clock with Alarm  
A stylish **digital clock** with AM/PM format and an **alarm feature**, built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.

     Features
 **Real-time Clock** – Updates every second  
 **12-Hour Format with AM/PM** – Displays time in a readable format  
 **Alarm Functionality** – Users can set an alarm, and it plays a sound when the time matches  
 **Date Display** – Shows the current date below the clock  
 **Modern UI** – Beautiful gradient background with a glassmorphism effect  
